title: IAA Tonight | NBA Drama & New Orleans Saints Preview
description: Kevin Durant continues to make headlines as his standoff with the Nets continues, meanwhile Ben Simmons and the Sixers settled on his grievance to recoup withheld pay from last season. Plus, we continue our previews of every NFL teams leading up to the season with a new era in New Orleans.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Ashley nicole moss, brandon marshall, lesean mccoy, Chantel Tremetiere)
